"title": "8215: confidence, results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8215",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God-given assurance produces spiritual maturity and stability, so that believers may withstand the adverse conditions of life.</p>\n<h2>Confidence in God's protection removes fear of disaster</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1-Ps46:2\">PSA 46:1–46:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:13-Exod14:14\">EXO 14:13–14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:3-Ps56:4\">PSA 56:3–56:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:22-Acts27:25\">ACT 27:22–27:25</a></p>\n<h2>Confidence in God's purposes produces hope</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:7\">PSA 130:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:3-Ps25:6\">PSA 25:3–25:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:5-Ps62:8\">PSA 62:5–62:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5-Ps71:7\">PSA 71:5–71:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:17-Prov23:18\">PRO 23:17–23:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:5\">ROM 5:3–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17-1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:17–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:17-Heb6:19\">HEB 6:17–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Confidence in God's presence makes his people bold</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:8-Isa41:10\">ISA 41:8–41:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:5-Josh1:9\">JOS 1:5–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:3-Ps3:6\">PSA 3:3–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:7\">PSA 20:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:4\">PSA 23:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1-Ps27:4\">PSA 27:1–27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:3\">PSA 138:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:2\">ISA 12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:8\">ISA 44:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:8\">JER 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:13\">ACT 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:27\">ACT 9:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:11\">ACT 18:9–18:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10-Eph6:11\">EPH 6:10–6:11</a></p>\n<h2>Confidence in God enables believers to endure difficulties</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:17-Hab3:19\">HAB 3:17–3:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10-2Tim3:11\">2TI 3:10–3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:26\">JOB 19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9-Ps42:10\">PSA 42:9–42:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:13\">EPH 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:32-Heb10:35\">HEB 10:32–10:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:35-Heb11:39\">HEB 11:35–11:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1-Heb12:2\">HEB 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:14\">1PE 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:12–4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:10\">REV 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Confidence in God leads to awareness of security</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1\">PSA 23:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10\">EPH 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:12\">DEU 33:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:9\">PSA 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:2\">PSA 40:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1-Ps46:3\">PSA 46:1–46:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:6-Ps112:8\">PSA 112:6–112:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:1-Ps121:2\">PSA 121:1–121:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:26\">PRO 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17\">ISA 32:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21\">2CO 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:13\">EPH 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:13\">1TI 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a></p>",
